race.comment: SEEIAYE (3) Russian Revolution colt from Blue Blazers on debut for the Peter Snowden yard. Has impressed in both trials and looks to have a good turn of foot. Winkers go on from the inside gate. Hard to stop. MYSTICAL (8) Exceed And Excel filly from Rainbow Falls on debut for the Michael Freedman stable. From a top juvenile yard and looked to have more to offer when second in an 818m trial at Warwick Farm. Maps well. ELIO (1) first starter by Ole Kirk out of Iconista from the Waterhouse & Bott stable. Looked good when a close-up second in an 818m trial at Warwick Farm. Expected to go well. JAIPUR MAISON (7) two-year-old filly by Zousain from the good producer Miss Amelia making her debut for the Waller stable. Fitted with the two trials and likely to go back from the awkward draw. Has a host of gear going on and look for her late. POMELO CHAMOMILE (9) Maurice filly from Barooda who makes debut on her home track for the Lees' yard. Sharp trial winner over 800m. Respect.
